Suicide Note.note_data:
BAK|s_tnn_papers|2~STR|To whoever finds this note:
forget about me, and forget
you saw this, my last missive
to a cruel world. This isn't
what I expected, and
certainly not what I asked
for. This is it... the end! I mean
it! No more living from this
point on. I'm all done, it's over
forever! That's it.|-77|-85|1|8600940|1
